500
00:43:52,040 --> 00:43:53,680
Yes.

501
00:43:53,680 --> 00:43:55,610
I'll leave it in your hands.

502
00:43:57,400 --> 00:43:59,210
You don't have to see me out.

503
00:44:08,140 --> 00:44:12,730
Mrs. Jang, you said you were going to the funeral today right?

504
00:44:12,730 --> 00:44:15,720
Take this on my behalf since I can't go in person.

505
00:44:15,720 --> 00:44:18,130
Mrs. Jang!

506
00:44:29,690 --> 00:44:31,920
You've had quite an ordeal.

507
00:44:31,920 --> 00:44:33,950
It's nothing.

508
00:44:35,360 --> 00:44:37,080
Sit.

509
00:44:40,340 --> 00:44:42,520
You said you're a doctor from England?

510
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:44,680
Yes.

511
00:44:44,680 --> 00:44:48,040
