513
00:44:55,540 --> 00:44:59,030
You're very straightforward.

514
00:45:00,120 --> 00:45:05,330
Hey, punk. You guys are misunderstanding this man.

515
00:45:07,430 --> 00:45:09,730
We apologize.

516
