Internally and externally it will show that you came in as an expert reference.

517
00:45:19,470 --> 00:45:24,670
You can go home soon, so don't worry, and make yourself comfortable.

518
00:45:24,670 --> 00:45:25,910
Thank you.

519
00:45:25,910 --> 00:45:29,980
And if anything has made you uncomfortable thus far, go ahead and tell me.

520
00:45:29,980 --> 00:45:32,650
Oh right. You have to eat.

521
00:45:32,650 --> 00:45:36,400
What do you like? Steak? Pasta?

522
00:45:36,400 --> 00:45:38,630
No. I'm okay.

523
00:45:47,560 --> 00:45:52,580
As you go through life, sometimes you get unlucky with bad situations out of nowhere.

524
00:45:52,580 --> 00:45:58,050
If you don't let those things go then it will only make things harder for you.

525
00:45:58,050 --> 00:46:02,270
After all, we'll be seeing each other again, right?

526
00:46:05,160 --> 00:46:07,670
Do you still not understand what I'm saying?

527
00:46:09,030 --> 00:46:13,940
I have a very close relationship with Chairman Lee Hwa Jeong.

528
00:46:13,940 --> 00:46:18,120
Her father-in-law, Chairman Seo, was my seonbae in high school.

529
00:46:21,570 --> 00:46:24,740
Do you not know because you're a foreigner?

530
00:46:24,740 --> 00:46:30,640
Anyway, let's go have a meal when things calm down.

531
00:46:39,930 --> 00:46:44,900
It's six o'clock, punk. Are you a chicken?

532
00:46:44,900 --> 00:46:49,640
Stand up straight!

533
00:46:49,640 --> 00:46:51,130
I-I-I'm sorry.

534
00:46:51,130 --> 00:46:54,330
What did the ancestors of the 9th generation of the Dumun Gongpa of the Hyeongju Bae clan,

535
00:46:54,330 --> 00:46:58,140
